Features:
The developed software does not only perform calculation; it also shows an error windows if any. Here is a list of the errors messages it can show:
‚Ä¢	Incorrect Credentials (in case of wrong username or password entry)
‚Ä¢	Spaces not allowed
‚Ä¢	All values must be positive
‚Ä¢	The timestamps must be in 24 hour format.
‚Ä¢	The timestamps must be a period of time of 60 minutes.
‚Ä¢	The input entered is not a numeric value.</p>
